# FormCMS React App Patterns

## Configuration
```typescript
// src/config.ts
export const CONFIG = { API_BASE_URL: import.meta.env.VITE_API_BASE_URL || '' };
```

## Authentication (Cookie-based)
All fetch calls MUST include `credentials: 'include'` — no exceptions.

| Method | Path | Body |
|--------|------|------|
| `GET`  | `/api/me` | — (check session) |
| `POST` | `/api/login` | `{ usernameOrEmail, password }` |
| `POST` | `/api/register` | `{ email, password, userName }` |
| `GET`  | `/api/logout` | — |
| `POST` | `/api/profile/password` | `{ oldPassword, password }` |

Create an `AuthContext` with `user`, `loading`, `login()`, `register()`, `logout()` and wrap `<App>` in `<AuthProvider>`. Call `GET /api/me` on mount to restore the session.

## Entity CRUD
```
GET    /api/entities/{entity}         – list (supports limit, offset, filters)
GET    /api/entities/{entity}/{id}    – single record
POST   /api/entities/{entity}/insert  – create
POST   /api/entities/{entity}/update  – update
POST   /api/entities/{entity}/delete  – delete
```

## Named Queries
```
GET /api/queries/{queryName}?param=value
```

